# My personal [Slate](https://github.com/jigish/slate) config.
#
# I use [Karabiner](https://pqrs.org/osx/karabiner/index.html.en) to bind
# individual keys to the obscene modifier cluster for triggering these.

# Not sure what this does. Someone recommended it.
config defaultToCurrentScreen true

# Make window hints show up for everything, with icons.
config windowHintsShowIcons
config windowHintsIgnoreHiddenWindows false
config windowHintsSpread

bind e:ctrl,alt,cmd,shift hint ASDFGHJKLQWERTYUIOPZXCVBNM
